Package net.minecraft.client.util

Class NetworkUtils

java.lang.Object
net.minecraft.client.util.NetworkUtils
public class NetworkUtils extends Object
A few client-side networking utilities.
Implementation Note:
This is not marked as client-only because it's used by the /publish command, which is only available to integrated servers yet was retained by proguard.
